<section class="support">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="large-12 large-centered columns">
      <h2 class="headline">
        We've got youcovered
      </h2>
      <p class="subhead">Community support and Handsontable experts at your service</p>

      <div class="row kinds-of-support">
        <div class="large-11 large-centered columns">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
              <svg class="community-support">
                <use xlink:href="#community_icon"></use>
              </svg>
              <div class="left desc">
                <h3>Community support</h3>
                <p>Get a helping hand from the active community on <a
                      href="https://github.com/handsontable/handsontable"
                      target="_blank">GitHub</a>, <a href="http://stackoverflow.com/tags/handsontable"
                      target="_blank">Stackoverflow</a> or <a
                      href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/handsontable"
                      target="_blank">Google Group</a> for free.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
              <svg class="priority-support">
                <use xlink:href="#help_icon"></use>
              </svg>
              <div class="left desc">
                <h3>Priority support</h3>
                <p>You'll get a guaranteed initial response within in 24 hours. Pay per incident or buy a subscription.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
              <svg class="dedicated-solutions">
                <use xlink:href="#cubes_icon"></use>
              </svg>
              <div class="left desc">
                <h3>Dedicated solutions</h3>
                <p>Our services are to help you solving problems. Whatever, whenever, we're on hand to help.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3>
        Contact us today
        <div class="border-bottom"></div>
      </h3>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="large-11 large-centered columns">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns">
              <div id="form-sent" class="notification success">Thanks for contacting us. We'll get back to you very soon.</div>
              <div id="form-error" class="notification error">Oops! We were unable to send the form.
                Please confirm the fields and submit them again.
              </div>

              <form id="contact-form" class="clearfix" action="https://my.handsontable.com/api/contact" method="post">
                <div class="selectbox">
                  <select required name="category">
                    <option value="" disabled selected>Select category</option>
                    <option value="general_question">General question</option>
                    <option value="technical_support">Technical support</option>
                    <option value="enterprise_inquiry">Enterprise/OEM inquiry</option>
                    <option value="request_for_quotation">Request for quotation</option>
                    <option value="request_for_quotation">Request for discount</option>
                    <option value="business_opportunity">Business opportunity</option>
                  </select>
                  <svg>
                    <use xlink:href="#arrow_down_icon"></use>
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <input type="hidden" placeholder="License ID" name="orderId"/>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Full name" name="name"/>
                <input type="text" placeholder="Company name" name="companyName"/>
                <input type="email" required placeholder="Email address" name="email"/>
                <textarea placeholder="Your message" required name="body"></textarea>
                <input type="hidden" name="returnTo" value="/support.html"/>
                <input type="submit" class="btn large blue right" value="Send"/>
              </form>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-offset-1 medium-5 columns">
              <h4>Multichannel support</h4>
              <p>We use a bunch of smart tools for seamless support. Whether you want to drop us a line on Skype, email,
                Google Hangout or somewhere else, we'll be there.</p>

              <h4>Guaranteed service levels</h4>
              <p>Time is a crucial to the success of most projects, which is why we always respond in under 24 hours.
                We're available Monday - Friday 8am-5pm (CET).</p>

              <h4>Experts at hand</h4>
              <p>As creators of Handsontable we know our solution inside out. That's why small and medium-sized enterprises trust us to fit
                 Handsontable to their other systems and processes. You can expect a short response time and the right
                 person for the right job.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>